     struct array
            ^~~~~
make: *** [all] Error 1
</code></pre>

<p>It seems as if the parser reads the "array" in <code>lhs.val.array</code> as <code>std::array</code> and treats the following <code>&lt;</code> as the start of a template list.</p>

